  <title>Concrete toolkit table component</title>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>table</emphasis> component is a component in which data is displayed and edited.
  </para>
  <para>
  	The format of a table component is a two-dimensional layout of cells which are organized into columns and
  	rows.
  </para>
  <para role="tip">
  	Please keep in mind that it is not possible to object map a single cell within the table component but to map the table component 
  	as a whole only. In order to interact with certain cells within the table component you have to use the according actions. 
  </para>
